ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Public Works and Government Services as the Minister for the purposes of that Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2019-390 of April 26, 2019; and (2) designating the MINISTER OF PUBLIC WORKS AND GOVERNMENT SERVICES, who is a member of the Queen's Privy Council for Canada and is not a member of the Treasury Board, as the Minister for the purposes of the FEDERAL PUBLIC SECTOR LABOUR RELATIONS ACT.
